 å®?ä½?\">weighted</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">value, then each server based on the value and number of connections under the current state to decide who will handle the user\'s request. Can give an example to illustrate her works:</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Suppose there are</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">n</span>-Font-family: Arial &quot;&gt; servers, each server in the <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">weighted</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">value of</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Wi (i = <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">1, 2... N),</span> session</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">for the</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Ci (i = 1, ... n), ALL-CONNECTIONS session