: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(RR),</span> Weighted Round-Robin <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(WRR),</span> Least-Connection <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(LC),</span> Weighted Least-Connection</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(WLC).</span> Questi quattro hanno le proprie norme di adattarsi all\'ambiente.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><b>Round-Robin:</b> <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Se la vostra scelta Ã¨ che l\'algoritmo <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">LLB,</span> sarÃ  equamente distribuiti i pacchetti del server, ha messo tutti i server sullo stesso piano, e non pratico a prendere in considerazione le differenze 