a\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Linux-kernel</span> in drie standaard controle in de keten van packet bestemming:</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">input, vooruit, de uitgang</span><html> T-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-Hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial &quot;&gt; <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">controle.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">input</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">is de datapakketten in de</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Linux toekomen</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">is het beheersen van de routering van de datapakketten,</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">output</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">uit de hand loopt pakketjes <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Linux.</span> Er zijn veel online artikelen over <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Ver