so-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">uiteindelijk beslist door <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">de</span> webserver waarop de desbetreffende zender. kunnen we verwijzen naar de <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">IPCHAINS-HOWTO.</span> In dit weinig gezegd.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"></span></p><html> pt; mso-paginering: weduwe-wees; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto &quot;&gt; <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><b><span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">2,</span> ipvsadm (www.linuxvirtualserver.org)</b> <br /> ipvsadm</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">wordt onderhouden door de jonge Chinese hackers, evolueerde hij van <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">ipportfw.</span></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">ipvsadm Linux</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">kernel wordt uitgevoerd, moet hij controleren om</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Linux</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">kernel <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">IP-routing</span> pakketten,</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">ipvsadm</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">voorwaarden die door de gebruiker datapakketten dienovereenkomstig. Leer</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">ipchains</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">gebruikers weten, in de</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Linux</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">kernel heeft drie controle pakketten in de plaats van bestemming keten: <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">input,</span></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">vooruit, output, ipvsadm</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">is in het proces van <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">doorstuurpakketten</span> voor de operatie.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">ipvsadm</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">rol is voor gebruikers om selecteert u de juiste</span><html> amilie: &quot;Verdana&quot;, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial &quot;&gt; <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">webserver server.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">LLB</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">in de keuze van vier verschillende regels, deze vier regels voor de selectie van die server te verzoeken af te handelen gebruiker:. Deze vier regels zijn</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Round-Robin <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(RR),</span> Weighted Round-Robin <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(WRR),</span> de minst-Connection <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(LC),</span> Weighted Least-Connection</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(WLC).</span> Deze vier hebben hun eigen regels aan te passen aan de omgeving.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><b>Round-robin:</b> <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Als uw keuze is dat het algoritme <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">LLB,</span> zal ze het worden gelijkmatig verdeeld server pakketten van, hij zet alle servers op dezelfde voet, en niet op praktische als rekening houden met de verschillen tussen de verschillende servers, zoals responstijd,</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">sessie</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">en het aantal! Bijvoorbeeld drie servers die u hebt <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">ABC,</span> dan is de distributie van datapakketten in de volgorde</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">LLB</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">is</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">...... ABCABCABC ..... <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">De voordelen van <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Round-Robin-algoritme</span> is eenvoudig, waarbij <u><a href=\"http://www.ixdba.net/a/os/\">het systeem</a></u> de middelen beperkt zijn, het nadeel is niet in staat om te detecteren welke server heeft een hogere respons, minder aansluitingen, dus hij is heel geschikt voor prestaties van de server omgeving.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"></span></p><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><b>in-bottom-alt:</b></span> auto &quot;&gt; <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><b>Weighted Round-Robin</b> <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Deze regel geldt voor gebruikers uit te breiden het systeem, omdat het de prestaties van servers in het cluster hebben een groter verschil tussen een server definitie voor elke parameter nodig is.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Dit is een geparametriseerd <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Round-Robin-algoritme,</span> parameter is de naam <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">gewogen.</span> U kunt, afhankelijk van de server de verwerking van uw vermogen toe te wijzen per server</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Gewogen</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">waarde, hoe hoger de waarde, hoe hoger de prioriteit, de standaard waarde is <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">1.</span> Bijvoorbeeld: je hebt drie servers, namelijk <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">A: 486, B:</span> Pentium, <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">C:</span> Pentium <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">2,</span> u kunt toewijzen</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Gewogen</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">waarde: <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">1, 2,</span></span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">3</span> </s<html> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">pan&gt;, is in overeenstemming met de</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Weighted</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Round-Robin-algoritme</span> bewerken van datapakketten in de volgorde van de servers <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">is:</span> CCCBBBA</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><br /> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Round-Robin</span> Weighted Round-Robin</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">is een speciaal geval, niet alleen alle servers hebben dezelfde</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Gewogen</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">waarde.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><b>Minst-Connection</b> <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Dit is een dynamisch algoritme, zal</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">LLB</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">worden gebaseerd op het huidige aantal verbindingen per server pakketten door te sturen, met ten minste aangesloten servers verzoek te behandelen de volgende. Dit is een goede allocatie algoritme kan alle stroom, voor de plotselinge verzoek of het verzoek kan glad maken een relatief groot aantal, en die geen van de gevraagde gegevens worden verzonden naar dezelfde server situatie.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><b>Gewogen kleinste-Connection</b> <br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Dit algoritme is een</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">minst-Connection Plannen van</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">een uitbreiding, werd ze toegewezen aan elke server een</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">gewogen</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">waarde, dan elke server op basis van de waarde en het aantal aansluitingen bij de huidige stand om te beslissen wie zal verzoek te behandelen van de gebruiker. Kan een voorbeeld geven om werken te illustreren haar:</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Stel dat er</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">n</span>-Font-family: Arial &quot;&gt; servers, elke server in de <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">gewogen</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">waarde van de</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Wi (i = <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">1, 2 ... N),</span> sessie</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">voor de</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Ci (i = 1, ... n), ALL-AANSLUITINGEN</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">en alle servers, zowel</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">C1 + C2 +....+</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Cn. sessie,</span> dan in overeenstemming met het volgende algoritme,</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">j</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">zal server te werken de volgende aanvraag:</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><br /> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(CJ</span> / ALL-AANSLUITINGEN) / Wj = min {(Ci / ALL-AANSLUITINGEN) / Wi} <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">(i</span> = 1, .., n)</span> </p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Kan ook worden vereenvoudigd tot:</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><br /> CJ / Wj = min {Ci / Wi} (i = 1, .., n)</span> </p><p align=\"left\" class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: left; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto\"> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Kunnen we een vergelijking maken van deze vier algoritmes,</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Round-Robin</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">en</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Weighted Round-Robin</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">is een statische methode, de huidige stand van de server niet kan maken een goede inschatting, dus de verdeling van de gegevens is niet de meest redelijke.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\"><br /></span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Echter, de prestaties van de server als de</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: \"Verdana\",\"sans-serif\"; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">Ronde-R</span> <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">in plaats van</span><html> OBiN <span style=\"font-family: å®?ä½?; font-size: 9pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ascii-font-family: Verdana; mso-hansi-font-family: Verdana; mso-bidi-font-family: å®?ä½?\">is de beste keuze.</span> <span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-fa